The paper discusses data hiding techniques for secure communication, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The techniques mentioned in the paper involve hiding information in various media, such as images and videos, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions cryptography and authentication, which are related to information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper involves analyzing and comparing different techniques, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
